<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Smart QR Codes for Your Business</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: #0b0f19;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .container {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 42px;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    h1 span {
      color: #6366f1;
    }
    p {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      max-width: 480px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: #6366f1;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .preview {
      background: #111827;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid #1f2937;
    }
    .qr {
      width: 140px;
      height: 140px;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        45deg,
        #000 0 10px,
        #222 10px 20px
      );
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .metric {
      background: #1f2937;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .metric strong {
      color: #22c55e;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <div>
      <h1>Trackable <span>QR Codes</span> That Bring You More Customers</h1>
      <p>I create custom QR codes with real analytics — see who scanned, when they scanned, and what they looked at.</p>
      <a class="btn" href="#">Get a Free Demo QR Code →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="preview">
      <div class="qr"></div>
      <div class="metric">Total scans: <strong>184</strong></div>
      <div class="metric">Unique visitors: <strong>129</strong></div>
      <div class="metric">Top device: <strong>iPhone</strong></div>
      <div class="metric">Peak time: <strong>5–7 PM</strong></div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
